@rajnamitha Upgrade to r1.2, and you will not face this issue. Also while using the transformed graph if you get following error in r1.2 :
tensorflow.python.framework.errors_impl.InvalidArgumentError: Retval[0] does not have value

Take off 'remove_nodes(op=Identity, op=CheckNumerics)' from the 'transforms' part, refer issue tensorflow/models#1721
